{
  "id": "adv_main_03_06_05",
  "title": "BIG4編1章30話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "living-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyodorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ行くよ？　せー……のっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ here we go. One‚ two…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "続けたい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We want to continue!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.533333079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "……ふふ、そっか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Fufu‚ I see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.466666603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり、みんな考えは同じでしたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As expected‚ everyone feels the same way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.7999999363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "不思議なものですわね。みんながなんと言うか\n聞く前から分かってしまうんですもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s strange‚ isn’t it? It’s like I knew\nwhat everyone was going to say before I even asked.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.833333524,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3599.999809299998,
          "startTime": 21.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あ、みんな見て見て！　まんまるなお月さま！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ look everyone! The moon is full!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4637.010638000003,
          "startTime": 26.0703439713
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルミュージックフェスの前に\n誓いを立てた日のような、いい月ですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a nice moon‚ like the one on the day\nwe made our vow before the Idol Music Festival.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.0036777515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、みんな。せっかくだし、外で話さない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ everyone. Since we’re here‚ why don’t we talk outside?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.3999879837,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_wind-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5866.666666699999,
          "startTime": 40.2666546504
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6300.009663899999,
          "startTime": 40.6999976476
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "garden-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 40.0166546504
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……風、気持ちいいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… The wind feels nice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.0666546504,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ね、なんだかほっとしたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei feels relieved‚ somehow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.0333175023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ちゃん……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei-chan…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.2333175023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_moon-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 51.0666498183
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんがいなくなったのは寂しいよ\nほんとに寂しい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sad that Kotono-chan’s gone.\nReally sad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.6333167393,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "だけど、芽衣は渚ちゃんも、沙季ちゃんも\nすずにゃんも大好き",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Mei loves Nagisa-chan‚ Saki-chan‚\nand Suzu-nyan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.3333192825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "だからね、みんなも月ストを続けたいって\n言ってくれて嬉しかった。……ほんとに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I was happy that you all said you wanted to\ncontinue Moon Tempest. …Really.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.5999877293,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "まったく、最近の芽衣は、らしくありませんわよ？\nそんなに湿っぽくなるなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly‚ you haven’t been yourself lately‚ Mei.\nGetting all sentimental like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.8333210627,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "……まぁ、事態が事態だから仕方ないとは思います\nですが、大事なのはこれからですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Well‚ I guess it can’t be helped‚ given the circumstances.\nBut what’s important is what we do from now on!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.9999877293,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "四人になって、ただただパフォーマンスが落ちたら\n意味がありませんからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no point in continuing as four\nif our performance just declines.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.3106839048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "四人でも……いえ、四人だからこそ出来る\nパフォーマンスを、強みを見つけていきましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s find a performance style that works for us as four…\nno‚ a performance style that only works because we’re four!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.3333210627,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんに何があったのかは分からないけど\n私は……いつか戻るって言った琴乃ちゃんを信じるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t know what happened to Kotono-chan‚\nbut I… believe her when she said she’d come back someday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2999851862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、琴乃ちゃんはなんにでも一生懸命で\n思い詰め過ぎちゃうところがあるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Kotono-chan puts her all into everything‚\nand she tends to overthink things‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.5999851862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "もし、琴乃ちゃんが自分自身をこれ以上\n思い詰めようとするなら……私が止める",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so if she tries to beat herself up\nany more than this… I’ll stop her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.4666503269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 124.2999834059
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃん……凄く頼もしいです\nきっと、琴乃ちゃんが見たらびっくりしますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa-chan… You’re so reliable.\nI’m sure Kotono-chan would be surprised if she saw you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.6999836603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "ただし、渚一人で止める必要はありませんわ\nその時は私達も一緒ですわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you don’t have to stop her alone.\nWe’ll be there with you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.3440810109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "それに、芽衣達が頑張ってたらさ、琴乃ちゃんも\nやっぱり戻りたいよーって思うかもしれないよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ if we work hard‚ maybe Kotono-chan will\nwant to come back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.0333169936,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "戻りたいと言ってきたら断ってあげますわ！\n……あー、やっぱり、戻してあげてもいいですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If she says she wants to come back‚ I’ll refuse!\n…Ah‚ actually‚ maybe we’ll let her come back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.9666641236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "私達でどりきゅんを倒せば\nきっと琴乃ちゃんは悔しがって戻って来ますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we beat DoriQyun‚\nKotono-chan will definitely come back out of frustration.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.1999734877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃんが強気だ……でも、うん、そうだよね\nそれくらいのつもりで頑張らないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki-chan is so confident… But yeah‚ you’re right.\nWe have to work hard with that in mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.0666401544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_05-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "私ね、ずっと琴乃ちゃんのことを\n後ろで支えようとばかりしてたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know‚ I’ve always been trying to\nsupport Kotono-chan from behind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.3666401544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
